              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">泡影</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/47826599/2e3cc81f7cf69d8fdf351f30e4e0993a_3848302022162671885.png",
                "id": "talent95489",
                "key": "星命定轨",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "星命定轨"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此角色为出战角色，我方执行「切换角色」行动时：</span>将此次切换视为「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">快速行动</span>」而非「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">战斗行动</span>」。（每回合1次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/47826599/a4683772d642e5af6323bd0a51d20fd7_8692351634923809853.png",
                "id": "talent35684",
                "key": "虚实流动",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "虚实流动"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方出战角色受到伤害时：</span>抵消1点伤害。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>，耗尽时不弃置此牌。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>弃置此牌，造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8633647648324258993.png",
                "id": "talent39052",
                "key": "虚影",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/1406b92c5115e3a534938a0d3638eeea_1189662593605536933.png",
                "title": "虚影"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_5033925645858867869.png",
                "id": "talent7289",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">泡影</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方造成技能伤害时：</span>移除此状态，使本次伤害加倍。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">快速行动</span></strong></p><p>执行了一次快速行动后，我方可以继续进行其他行动。</p><p>只有执行了一次战斗行动后，才会轮到对方行动。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">战斗行动</span></strong></p><p>我方执行了一次战斗行动后，会轮到对方行动。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">打出具有此规则的手牌是一个战斗行动，而非快速行动。</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/24/47826599/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_116955948269862411.png",
